### Pokémon Sprites — Missing Assets

Create a dedicated Markdown file (`missing-sprites.md`) that catalogues every Pokémon whose sprite asset is currently missing or unrenderable in the app.

The file should include:

- Pokémon name and Dex number
- Which variants are missing (default, shiny, shadow, mega, regional, costume)
- Source URL where the sprite should be fetched or confirmed
