## Gstack Integration

This project lives inside the **SecondBrain** Obsidian vault, which has [gstack](../gstack.md) installed and active globally at `~/.claude/skills/gstack`.

gstack gives Claude Code 23 specialist slash-command roles. Use the following sprint order when building TrainerDex:

```
/office-hours       ← reframe and challenge each feature before building
/autoplan           ← CEO + design + engineering review in one command
build               ← implement
/review             ← staff engineer catches bugs that pass CI
/qa https://...     ← QA lead with real Chromium browser
/ship               ← open PR with tests
/land-and-deploy    ← merge → CI → verify production
/retro              ← weekly retrospective
